Help your relationship managers connect dots easily by using the Onboarding and Know Your Customer data models. These models help businesses efficiently capture the details of beneficial owners, controlling parties, and business structure hierarchy.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions where Financial Services Sales Cloud and Business Client Engagement are enabled.

Why: To go through your clientâ€™s complex corporate landscape can be challenging, and it often leads to trust and integrity issues. The ultimate ownership information is critical in the process of onboarding clients, suppliers, and partners.

How: In Setup, search for and select Business Client Engagement Settings. Turn on Business Client Engagement.

Salesforce Help: Business Client Engagement
Setup of Business Client Engagement
title: Understanding Ultimate Owners for Business Clients
